eu.kidf.diversicon.core

Class ExtractedStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.kidf.diversicon.core.ExtractedStream

  • public class ExtractedStream
extends Object
    A stream possibly extracted from a compressed sourceUrl. Use {#stream()} to get the stream to consume. If you need to consume the stream several times, call toTempFile() first.
    Since:
    0.1.0
